game.name: Steel Head
game.description:
Another beautifully-designed, fun-filled adventure game is waiting for you! All you need is just join Steel Head and get yourself ready to feel the thrill and entertainment you have not experienced for long! In this free online game for kids, you will have to help this steelhead to collect the munchies as assigned for a particular level. The good news is that those nuclear containers seem to be quite crunchy. Hurry up, boys! Play it in your favourite and set your own record!

There are 15 different levels where you can expect to face off new challenge in each level. The number of munchies will vary from level to level. Make sure to collect all of them to complete your level. Also try to clear the level in the shortest possible time to earn a good score. Your munchies can be available at different locations of the screen. So, apply your patience and concentration skills to grab all of them and move to the next level. 

In this cool jumping game for kids, you have to use left and right arrow keys to move and UP key to jump. Feel free to press the UP twice to complete the double jump! Press R mentioned at the right bottom of the screen to reply your game! You can also enjoy this one of the best adventure games for boys in both desktop and mobile phones. Hope you have enjoyed a lot during the gameplay! Looking for more complex platform games? Check out the adventure category for boys to take your fantasy to the new level!
